docs.text: the story goes like this .

docs.text: edward norton is an insomniac trying to enlighten his dull life by going to a variety of disease therapy sessions , until he meets marla ( helena bonham carter ) .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: norton claims that she is wrecking his pleasurable lifestyle , when he spots her at a session that he also attended .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: apparently the disease sessions help them see what life is like , literally living in pain .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: why any person would think of such a thing is beyond me , but things do get worse .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: norton is soon assigned to a job that calls for traveling , and it's on a plane that he meets tyler durden ( brad pitt ) .
docs.label: negative

docs.text: the two men develop a bond , and go out to a bar , and by golly after they get drunk , the two pitiful characters fight .

docs.text: anyway , their fighting catches other pathetic loser's attention , and a club is formed .
